{"title":"Docker 常用镜像部署","uid":"75dacad14e098df2be0901cfbf963953","slug":"Docker 常用镜像部署","date":"2022-04-15T11:50:34.000Z","updated":"2022-06-29T06:29:45.099Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Docker 常用镜像部署.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"docker-rabbitmq\"><a href=\"#docker-rabbitmq\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"docker rabbitmq\"></a>docker rabbitmq</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">docker run --privileged --restart&#x3D;always -it -d --hostname&#x3D;rabbitmq --name&#x3D;rabbitmq -e RABBITMQ_DEFAULT_USER&#x3D;twitf -e RABBITMQ_DEFAULT_PASS&#x3D;twitf -p 15672:15672 rabbitmq\n\n\nrabbitmq-plugins enable --offline rabbitmq_mqtt rabbitmq_federation_management rabbitmq_stomp rabbitmq_management_agent\n\n\ncd  &#x2F;etc&#x2F;rabbitmq&#x2F;conf.d&#x2F;\necho management_agent.disable_metrics_collector &#x3D; false &gt; management_agent.disable_metrics_collector.conf </code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"docker-mariadb\"><a href=\"#docker-mariadb\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"docker mariadb\"></a>docker mariadb</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">docker run -it -d --name mariadb -e MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD&#x3D;root -p 3306:3306 mariadb</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"docker-elasticsearch\"><a href=\"#docker-elasticsearch\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"docker elasticsearch\"></a>docker elasticsearch</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">docker run -d --name es -p 9200:9200 -p 9300:9300 -e &quot;discovery.type&#x3D;single-node&quot; elasticsearch:latest</code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">docker run --name mongo -p 27017:27017 -d mongo</code></pre>\n\n<h1 id=\"redis\"><a href=\"#redis\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"redis\"></a>redis</h1><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">docker run --name redis -p 6379:6379 -d redis redis-server --appendonly yes</code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">docker  run --name nacos -d -p 8848:8848 --privileged&#x3D;true --restart&#x3D;always -e JVM_XMS&#x3D;256m -e JVM_XMX&#x3D;256m -e MODE&#x3D;standalon</code></pre>\n\n<h1 id=\"Nacos\"><a href=\"#Nacos\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Nacos\"></a>Nacos</h1><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">docker run --env PREFER_HOST_MODE&#x3D;hostname --privileged --restart&#x3D;always -it -d --env MODE&#x3D;standalone --env NACOS_AUTH_ENABLE&#x3D;true --name nacos -p 8848:8848 nacos&#x2F;nacos-server</code></pre>\n<h1 id=\"beanstalkd-延迟队列\"><a href=\"#beanstalkd-延迟队列\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"beanstalkd(延迟队列)\"></a>beanstalkd(延迟队列)</h1><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">docker run --privileged --restart&#x3D;always -it -d -p 11300:11300 schickling&#x2F;beanstalkd</code></pre>\n\n","text":"docker rabbitmqdocker run --privileged --restart&#x3D;always -it -d --hostname&#x3D;rabbitmq --name&#x3D;rabbitmq -e RABBITMQ_DEFAULT_USER&#...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.3k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Docker","slug":"Docker","count":1,"path":"api/categories/Docker.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Docker","slug":"Docker","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Docker.json"},{"name":"DockerImages","slug":"DockerImages","count":1,"path":"api/tags/DockerImages.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#docker-rabbitmq\"><span class=\"toc-text\">docker rabbitmq</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#docker-mariadb\"><span class=\"toc-text\">docker mariadb</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#docker-elasticsearch